        <abstract> 
<p>Looks forward to the paper on CD’s edible fungus specimen from Tierra del Fuego [read 16 Mar 1841; <hi rend="italic">Trans. Linn. Soc. Lond.</hi> 19 (1845): 37–43].</p>  
<p>Sends a correction: <hi rend="italic">Fagus betuloides</hi>, not <hi rend="italic">F. antarctica</hi>, is the common tree of Tierra del Fuego.</p> 
        </abstract>
